divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking a picture of a hotair balloon, since I don't see them much in this area. I work in the mountains of Western North Carolina and was driving on I-40 I took this picture right outside of Asheville with my cell phone. I didn't notice another object in the picture until I downloaded it on my computer. I was very surprised to see this image. Could you please tell me what it is.
